---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Eccentric Echoes" description="Discover the whimsical world of Eccentric Echoes, where we explore human quirks through a lens of psychedelic futurism, blending humor, insight, and vibrant storytelling to illuminate the extraordinary in the everyday.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 via-indigo-800 to-violet-900 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent rounded-full mix-blend-soft-light filter blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-primary rounded-full mix-blend-soft-light filter blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-6 text-sm font-bold text-accent bg-black bg-opacity-30 rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm animate-pulse">
          PSYCHEDELIC FUTURISM
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          About <span class="text-accent">Eccentric</span> Echoes
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
          Unveiling the Wild Side of Human Quirks with Humor and Insight
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Welcome Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950 to-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative p-8 md:p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/50 to-violet-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-3xl border border-purple-500/30 shadow-2xl shadow-purple-500/20">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="fas fa-stars text-2xl text-black"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">Welcome to Eccentric Echoes</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-invert">
            <p class="text-purple-100 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              In a universe where reality bends like a cosmic rubber band, <strong class="text-accent">Eccentric Echoes</strong> emerges as your portal to the psychedelic futurism of the human experience. We're not just a blog—we're a swirling vortex of curiosity, where the mundane morphs into the mesmerizing, and every quirk of humanity is celebrated with a dash of wit and a splash of wonder.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-indigo-950">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Our <span class="text-accent">Vision</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-2xl opacity-20 blur-lg animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/50 to-violet-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-500/30 h-full">
            <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 leading-relaxed">
              Imagine a future where neon dreams collide with ancient echoes of the soul. That's the theme pulsing through our veins: <em class="text-accent font-bold">psychedelic futurism</em>. We dive deep into the oddities that make us human—from bizarre habits and eccentric inventions to the hilarious mishaps of modern life—all viewed through a kaleidoscope of innovative, mind-expanding perspectives.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/50 to-indigo-800/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-500/30 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Mind Expansion</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-200">Challenging perceptions through unconventional storytelling</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-900/50 to-purple-800/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-500/30 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 mt-12">
            <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-laugh"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Humor & Insight</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-200">Finding laughter in life's quirkiest moments</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/50 to-violet-800/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-500/30 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-infinity"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Endless Curiosity</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-200">Exploring the infinite spectrum of human experience</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-800/50 to-indigo-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-500/30 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 mt-12">
            <div class="text-accent text-4xl mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Vibrant Storytelling</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-200">Painting words with the colors of imagination</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950 to-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Our <span class="text-accent">Mission</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent rounded-3xl"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/50 to-violet-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-purple-500/30">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent mb-6">
                  <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-2xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Illuminate</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-200">Shedding light on the extraordinary hiding in plain sight</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent mb-6">
                  <i class="fas fa-heart text-2xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Celebrate</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-200">Honoring the beautiful chaos of human individuality</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent mb-6">
                  <i class="fas fa-rocket text-2xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Inspire</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-200">Propelling minds toward new realms of possibility</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-16 text-center">
              <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                At <span class="text-accent font-bold">Eccentric Echoes</span>, we believe that the most profound truths are often discovered through laughter, wonder, and the courage to see the world through different lenses. Join us on this cosmic journey where every human quirk becomes a constellation in the vast galaxy of shared experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 via-indigo-800 to-violet-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Ready to Explore the Eccentric?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-200 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join our community of curious minds and never miss a beat of our psychedelic adventures.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/articles" class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent text-black font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/50 inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-compass mr-2"></i> Explore Articles
          </a>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-full border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm transform hover:scale-105 inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i> Join the Echo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>